Simple tracker of days spent in locations time-limited by a visa.
It automatically logs which country you are in every day.
It reminds you when you are close to the limit.
It stores all data locally on your device.


Installation on Android(not for ios):
Open the app URL in Chrome on your Android device.
Tap the menu and select “Add to Home screen” to install it as an app(it's not native but a progressive web app).
Grant permissions when prompted.


